channel.title: K so i really need help,
channel.description:
k so i really need help, My server WILL NOT go online. I have port forwarded, done no-ip, checked firewall settings, had many people help me, but none of them can figure out what the problem is. i REALLY want to host my own rsps but i cannot pay money to have anyone help me, i don't have a money source.
PLEASE, can someone teamview me or something andhelp me figure out what the deal is, cause it needs to be fixed..
